1>\n              <p className=\"text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8 px-4\">\n                Lamentamos que no est├®s conforme con tu compra. Al iniciar este proceso, **congelaremos el pago del vendedor** y nuestro equipo de soporte se pondr├í en contacto contigo.\n              </p>\n\n              <div className=\"bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-3xl border border-red-100 mb-8 flex items-start gap-3 text-left\">\n                <ShieldAlert className=\"w-5 h-5 text-red-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" />\n                <div>\n                  <p className=\"text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-red-600 mb-1\">Flujo de Garant├¡a</p>\n                  <p className=\"text-[10px] text-red-800 leading-tight\">\n                    Una vez iniciada la solicitud, el monto no se liberar├í al vendedor hasta que se resuelva la disputa. Deber├ís enviar fotos de la prenda a <span className=\"font-bold\">soporte@modacircular.com</span>.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <button\n                onClick={handleSubmit}\n                disabled={status === 'loading'}\n                className=\"w-full py-4 bg-red-600 text-white rounded-full text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest shadow-xl hover:bg-red-700 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2\"\n              >\n                {status === 'loading' ? <Loader2 className=\"animate-spin h-5 w-5\" /> : 'Bloquear Pago y Notificar'}\n              </button>\n\n              {status === 'error' && (\n                <p className=\"mt-4 text-xs text-red-500 font-bold\">{errorMsg}</p>\n              )}\n              \n              <Link href=\"/\" className=\"inline-block mt-6 text-xs text-muted hover:text-primary transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest\">\n                Cancelar y Volver\n              </Link>\n            </div>\n          )}\n\n          {status === 'success' && (\n            <div className=\"animate-in zoom-in fade-in duration-500\">\n              <div className=\"w-24 h-24 bg-red-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6\">\n                <Mail className=\"w-12 h-12 text-red-600\" />\n              </div>\n              \n              <h2 className=\"text-3xl font-serif text-primary mb-3\">Solicitud Enviada</h2>\n              <p className=\"text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mb-10 px-4\">\n                Hemos bloqueado la liberaci├│n de fondos para esta prenda. Por favor, revisa tu correo electr├│nico con las instrucciones para proceder con la devoluci├│n f├¡sica y el reembolso.\n              </p>\n\n              <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n                <Link \n                  href=\"/\"\n                  className=\"w-full py-4 bg-primary text-cream rounded-full text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest shadow-lg hover:bg-primary/90 flex items-center justify-center gap-2\"\n                >\n                  <Home className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n                  Ir al Inicio\n                </Link>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          )}\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </main>\n  );\n}\n","usedDeprecatedRules":[]},{"filePath":"C:\\Users\\cmont\\OneDrive (1)\\Documentos\\Montidigital\\Proyectos Antigravity\\Venta Ropa de Segunda\\app\\page.tsx","messages":[{"ruleId":"@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars","severity":1,"message":"'Button' is defined but never used. Allowed unused vars must match /^_/u.","line":3,"column":10,"nodeType":"Identifier","messageId":"unusedVar","endLine":3,"endColumn":16,"suggestions":[{"messageId":"removeUnusedImportDeclaration","data":{"varName":"Button"},"fix":{"range":[104,153],"text":""},"desc":"Remove unused import declaration."}]},{"ruleId":"@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars","severity":1,"message":"'e' is defined but never used.","line":22,"column":14,"nodeType":"Identifier","messageId":"unusedVar","endLine":22,"endColumn":15},{"ruleId":"@next/next/no-img-element","severity":1,"message":"Using `<img>` cou